OL,3,CGuernsey Post to cut ten jobs in
OL,4,Cefficiency savings
OL,6,FGuernsey Post will cut ten jobs as it
OL,7,Frestructures to try and make
OL,8,Fefficiency savings.
OL,10,FFrom September, the company's freight
OL,11,Fsubsidiary HR Air will be split, with
OL,12,FGuernsey deliveries brought into the
OL,13,Fisland's main postal operations, while
OL,14,FHR Air's customer services and admin
OL,15,Fwill move to Jersey.
OL,17,FGuernsey Post Chief Executive Steve
OL,18,FSheridan says they will support all
OL,19,Fworkers affected by redundancy and the
OL,20,FHR brand continues to be an important
OL,21,Fpart of the wider business.
