OL,3,CGuernsey Post to cut ten jobs in
OL,4,Cefficiency savings
OL,6,FHe explains: "This has been a very
OL,7,Fdifficult decision, but a necessary
OL,8,Fone to respond to changing market
OL,9,Fdynamics and ensure we are operating
OL,10,Fin a way that is both efficient and
OL,11,Fsustainable.
OL,13,F"Our priority is to support our
OL,14,Fcolleagues through this transition
OL,15,Fwhile continuing to deliver reliable
OL,16,Fand high-quality service to our
OL,17,Fcustomers."
